<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
HOUSEHOLD AND PERSONAL-CARE PRODUCTS (HHP)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- Colgate-Palmolive Co. said it completed the
$172 million acquisition of Javex Cos. from Bristol-Myers
Squibb Co. Javex is a leading maker of bleach and fabric
softener in Canada.
</LP>
