   Big Board Seats Are Sold
</HL>
<DATE>
04/09/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<IN>
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
SECURITIES INDUSTRY (SCR)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- A New York Stock Exchange seat sold for
$395,000 Friday, up $5,000 from two previous sales earlier in
the day.
   The last prior seat sale before Friday was for $360,000 on
March 13. Currently, the bid price for Big Board seats is
$360,000, while the asking price is $450,000.
</LP>
