<LP>
   DALLAS -- Comstock Resources Inc. said it registered with
the Securities and Exchange Commission to offer 2.5 million
common shares.
   Proceeds will be used to repay the company's $9.8 million
in bank debt, to complete 95 oil and gas wells and to acquire
additional oil and gas properties.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Eppler, Guerin &amp; Turner Inc. of Dallas is managing the
underwriting.
